Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I deleted a week's worth of code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.64,0:00:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.50,0:00:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Because it had been right for the wrong reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.72,0:00:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.29,0:00:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}After yesterday's 90 percent win rate illusion collapsed, I made the most against-my-own-instincts decision I could — delete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Not bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The things I'd been right about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A week of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I hardcoded the grid feature off inside the system config.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No future version of the code can turn it back on without me physically editing the system file.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.05,0:00:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ulysses pact with my future self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then I wrote a new house rule — every strategy change requires a 90-day backtest before it touches a dollar.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Performers protect their past rightness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.65,0:00:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Learners replace it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:01:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The ability to burn something you were right about — that's the thing that separates real learning from performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 8 tomorrow — I told everyone I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.61,0:01:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
